  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/6d6f9c66c54bdb092aed0f763399cf9f.poster.avif?t=1723634731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/6d6f9c66c54bdb092aed0f763399cf9f.webm?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/6d6f9c66c54bdb092aed0f763399cf9f.mp4?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Cat and Ghostly Road is an atmospheric point-and-click quest in which you play as a white cat.<br><br>Once the painter saved the cat, and they began to live together. But one day a misfortune happened to the man.<br><br>You need to help the man and save him from death. To do this, you have to go on a dangerous journey to the world of ghosts and demons.<br><br>Not all things are what they seems: in order to see their true form, you have a special vision.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/0ca0aa3df16d8f9f94d34e269eedb990.poster.avif?t=1723634731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/0ca0aa3df16d8f9f94d34e269eedb990.webm?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/0ca0aa3df16d8f9f94d34e269eedb990.mp4?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/6d6f9c66c54bdb092aed0f763399cf9f.poster.avif?t=1723634731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/6d6f9c66c54bdb092aed0f763399cf9f.webm?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/6d6f9c66c54bdb092aed0f763399cf9f.mp4?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Cat and Ghostly Road is an atmospheric point-and-click quest in which you play as a white cat.<br><br>Once the painter saved the cat, and they began to live together. But one day a misfortune happened to the man.<br><br>You need to help the man and save him from death. To do this, you have to go on a dangerous journey to the world of ghosts and demons.<br><br>Not all things are what they seems: in order to see their true form, you have a special vision.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/0ca0aa3df16d8f9f94d34e269eedb990.poster.avif?t=1723634731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/0ca0aa3df16d8f9f94d34e269eedb990.webm?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994340/extras/0ca0aa3df16d8f9f94d34e269eedb990.mp4?t=1723634731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
